beer.beer_description: We’re levelling up this DIPA with an experimental hop expansion pack. Newbies Strata and Zappa attack with a fruity onslaught of passion-fruit and strawberry and their secret weapons dank resin and mint. The high scoring combo of tropical fruit and pine is delivered super smoothly via wheat and oats. Low bitterness, a solid malt base and no-holds barred hopping leaves Arcade Made top of the leader board every time.
